## GROUP BY
```SQL
SELECT 
 A.Color
 ,SUM(a.ListPrice) AS Suma --agregamos un alias para la nueva seccion
FROM
	Production.Product AS a
GROUP BY
	a.Color

```

#### Adding more columns
```
SELECT 
 A.Color
 ,a.Name -- Add to SELECT and remember add to GROUP BY Selection
 ,SUM(a.ListPrice) AS Suma --agregamos un alias para la nueva seccion
FROM
	Production.Product AS a
GROUP BY
	a.Color
	,a.Name
```
